<li id="cite_note-6"><b><a href="#cite_ref-6">^</a></b> <a href="http://www.collegehumor.com/video:1945421" class="external free" rel="nofollow">http://www.collegehumor.com/video:1945421</a></li>
<li id="cite_note-7"><b><a href="#cite_ref-7">^</a></b> <span class="citation" id="CITEREFKlimaBellugi1979"><a href="/wiki/Edward_Klima" title="Edward Klima">Klima, Edward S.</a>; <a href="/wiki/Ursula_Bellugi" title="Ursula Bellugi">Bellugi, Ursula</a> (1979), <i>The signs of language</i>, Boston: Harvard University Press, <a href="/wiki/International_Standard_Book_Number" title="International Standard Book Number">ISBN</a>&#160;<a href="/wiki/Special:BookSources/9780674807969" title="Special:BookSources/9780674807969">9780674807969</a></span><span class="Z3988" title="ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Abook&amp;rft.genre=book&amp;rft.btitle=The+signs+of+language&amp;rft.aulast=Klima&amp;rft.aufirst=Edward+S.&amp;rft.au=Klima%2C%26%2332%3BEdward+S.&amp;rft.au=Bellugi%2C%26%2332%3BUrsula&amp;rft.date=1979&amp;rft.place=Boston&amp;rft.pub=Harvard+University+Press&amp;rft.isbn=9780674807969&amp;rfr_id=info:sid/en.wikipedia.org:American_Sign_Language"><span style="display: none;">&#160;</span></span></li>
<li id="cite_note-8"><b><a href="#cite_ref-8">^</a></b> Walker, Lou Ann. (1987). A Loss for Words: The Story of Deafness in a Family. New York: HarperPerennial. p. 31. <a href="/wiki/Special:BookSources/0060914254" class="internal mw-magiclink-isbn">ISBN 0-06-091425-4</a>.</li>
<li id="cite_note-9"><b><a href="#cite_ref-9">^</a></b> Barbara F. Grimes and Joseph Evans Grimes.<i>Ethnologue</i>. page 361 (2000, Summer Institute of Linguistics International, ISBN 155671103)</li>
</ol>
</div>
