<li>Acredolo, Linda, &amp; Goodwyn, Susan. (2008) "Baby Signs: The Original Sign Language Program for Babies." Retrieved from <a href="http://www.babysigns.com/index.cfm?id=61" class="external free" rel="nofollow">http://www.babysigns.com/index.cfm?id=61</a></li>
<li>Barnard, Henry (1852), "Tribute to Gallaudet—A Discourse in Commemoration of the Life, Character and Services, of the Rev. Thomas H. Gallaudet, LL.D.— Delivered Before the Citizens of Hartford, January 7, 1852. With an Appendix, Containing History of Deaf-Mute Instruction and Institutions, and other Documents." (Download book: <a href="http://www.saveourdeafschools.org/tribute_to_gallaudet.pdf" class="external free" rel="nofollow">http://www.saveourdeafschools.org/tribute_to_gallaudet.pdf</a> Saveourdeafschools.org)</li>
